    <item>
      <title>阿拉伯分裂阻碍美国反击胡塞武装船只袭击的努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/red-sea-shipping-attacks-divisions-hinder-us-efforts-to-counter-yemen-houthis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，由于华盛顿的阿拉伯盟友之间存在分歧，美国打击也门胡塞叛军的努力遇到了重大障碍，因为也门胡塞叛军袭击了世界上最重要水道之一的船只。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/red-sea-shipping-attacks-divisions-hinder-us-efforts-to-counter-yemen-houthis</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 09:00:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将从 2027 年起对钢铁进口征收气候税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/uk-to-introduce-carbon-border-tax-from-2027-after-move-by-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继欧盟采取类似举措后，英国将从 2027 年起对来自气候制度较弱国家的进口排放密集型商品征收碳边境税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-18/uk-to-introduce-carbon-border-tax-from-2027-after-move-by-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 07:55:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
