    <item>
      <title>疲惫的智利人拒绝第二部宪法提案，对该国政治阶层造成打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/chile-rejects-second-proposed-constitution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[智利拒绝了多年来第二次新宪法提案，延长了不确定性，并凸显了该国政治制度未能将社会不满情绪转化为一套新的基本法律。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/chile-rejects-second-proposed-constitution</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 22:40:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚领导人的政党赢得快速投票，扩大统治地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/serbia-s-strongman-oversees-another-election-win-for-his-populist-party</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚总统亚历山大·武契奇的政党在周日的提前选举中取得了巨大胜利，巩固了这位巴尔干领导人在该国长达十年的统治地位，因为该国正在不稳定地走向欧盟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-17/serbia-s-strongman-oversees-another-election-win-for-his-populist-party</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 20:52:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
